g="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Column" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para" /><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="0" Right="0" Top="0" /><SHAPECOMMENT>전재윤</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{rm{DIY}it}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>(디아이와이)는 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="8534333" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="574972"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="7250" WidthRelTo="Absolute" /><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para" /><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0" /><SHAPECOMMENT>전재윤</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>rm Do~ {i}t ~Yourself</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>의 약어로, 소비자가 직접 제품을 만들어 사용하는 것을 말한다. 자신만의 개성과 취향을 추구하는 소비자가 늘어나고, 온라인을 통해 지식과 정보를 쉽게 공유할 수 있게 되면서 소품, 가구 등을 직접 만들어 사용하는 경우가 많아지고 있다. </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="24880990" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="278461"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1937" WidthRelTo="Absolute" /><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Column" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para" /><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="0" Right="0" Top="0" /><SHAPECOMMENT>전재윤</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{rm{DIY}it}`</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>는 제작 과정에서 많은 시간과 노력이 필요하지만 원하는 대로 제품을 만드는 즐거음을 준다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>(1) 모둠별로 수가 포함되어 있는 제품 중에서 어떤 제품을 만들지 정해 보자.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>(2) 유리수와 순환소수, 식의 계산과 관련된 문제로 제품 안의 수를 표현하여 제품을 만들어 보자.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>(3) 모둠별로 만든 제품을 발표하고, 친구들과 함께 과정을 되돌아보자.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0" ColumnBreak="true" PageBreak="false"><TEXT CharShape="1"><ENDNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><AUTONUM Number="3" NumberType="Endnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar="." Superscript="false" Type="Digit" /></AUTONUM><CHAR> [정답] (1) 유한소수 (2) 무한소수</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0" /></P><P ParaShape="1" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>[해설]</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></ENDNOTE></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>다음을 보고, 괄호 안의 알맞은 것에 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="24158991" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="538872"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="750" WidthRelTo="Absolute" /><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Column" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para" /><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="0" Right="0" Top="0" /><SHAPECOMMENT>전재윤</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{rm{O}it}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>표를 하시오.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>(1) </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="8534333" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="574972"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2012" WidthRelTo="Absolute" /><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Column" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para" /><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="0" Right="0" Top="0" /><SHAPECOMMENT>전재윤</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>1.35`</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>는 소수점 아래에 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="16527168" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="278461"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="662" WidthRelTo="Absolute" /><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Column" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para" /><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="0" Right="0" Top="0" /><SHAPECOMMENT>전재윤</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>0`</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>이 아닌 숫자가 유한 번 나타나므로 (유한소수, 무한소수)이다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>(2) </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="9256332" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="314561"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="5761" WidthRelTo="Absolute" /><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Column" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para" /><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="0" Right="0" Top="0" /><SHAPECOMMENT>전재윤</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>0.424242`cdots`</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>는 소수점 아래에 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="18770277" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="538872"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="662" WidthRelTo="Absolute" /><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAn